reviewText: I received my DVD photography Hints tips today. I was surprised with the 13 min content. its very short and doesn't wroth the $39.95 and if i would know its like that i won't buy it with $10. I really hate it and would like to return it back to you.
Not much content to challenge the experienced photographer. The title is a bit of an "over-reach". This is a short "how to..." sort of a merit badge in basic picture taking.
